<p>
<lb n="1"/>tirumakaḷ pola perunilac celviyum taṉakke yurimai pūṇṭamai <unclear>maṉakkoḷa</unclear>k kān taḷūrccā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>lai kalamaṟuttaruḷi veṅkai nāṭuṅ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kaṅkapāṭiyum nuḷampa pāṭiyum ta
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭikaiṉiyomum <hi rend="grantha">po</hi>ṉāmum<note n="304-1">There is apparently a mistake here and the continuation of the passage up to line 5 is lost.</note>
<lb n="5"/>yāṇṭu [ <num value="27">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 7</num><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>vatu maturā] ntaka catu<hi rend="grantha">rve</hi>timaṅkalattu
<lb n="6"/>vaṭapiṭākai māvaṇṭur <hi rend="grantha">de</hi>varu māntai nakkarkku <unclear>viṭṭa</unclear>
<lb n="7"/>nuntā viḷakku Oṉṟiṉāl vaitta Āṭu toṇṇūru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

